{"title":"澳门走笔","authors":["石英"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":6,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"澳门走笔（两首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石英"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈祖阁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背靠山脊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对海涛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五百年缕缕不绝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香火如雾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庙终是中国庙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然地面屈姓“葡”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五百年祈祷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍然割裂如初。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日回归在即，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃一支巨型蜡烛？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜泪淋漓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜡花如兔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五百年的妈祖庙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"澳门之祖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看新的妈祖雕像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矗立半岛高处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着金门，望着台湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着大洋中每一根桅杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲人归来兮……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大三巴牌坊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨日的辉煌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人道曾经是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远东最大的天主教堂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在此寄踪者赫赫："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"利玛窦、汤若望……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少人拾级留影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"观光者川流不息；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恍惚间仿佛是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年盛时期善男信女。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1835年一场大火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几乎将教堂夷为平地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只剩一道胸墙兀立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣讲占领者存在的理由："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡不离去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听者不语。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只见背后壁画寥落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有玻璃匣中藏秘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空气已凝固多时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像匣中枯骨一样静寂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“春”去也，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大自然也在换季，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下这牌坊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉后人曾经有过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管早已是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"断垣残壁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者为作家、人民日报社高级编辑）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}